  "text": "The initial value of δ is set to zero, which allows us to find the parameters V P0 and ε from V nmo;P and η. The density ρ and shearwave vertical velocity V S0 (if only PP data are available) for the initial model are supposed to be found from well logs. Potentially, the accuracy of the initial model can be improved by using velocityindependent layer stripping [CITATION_1] .",
